front.title: •I Must Be Allowed To Speak (V)
front.gametext: Deploy on table. Once per character, when you deploy Chewie, Lando, Leia, or Luke to a Tatooine site, may take any one card from Used Pile into hand; reshuffle. While Han is frozen, Rebels are immune to None Shall Pass. Once per game, may deploy a farm from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)

pulledBy: We Wish To Board At Once
